  SHET is the multiuser multilanguage spreadsheet which offers SC3
   functionality. All the capability of the world's most popular business
   software are now available under UNIX/UTIX. Familiar DOS applications
   can be combined with the power of the UTIX system.

  Integrated spreadsheet and graphics provide a consistent user
   interface. Reports can be generated quickly and easily using TBL
   and NROFF.

  Multilanguage menu, help, message system supports now english and
   russian languages and is fully configurable.

  Terminal and printer graphics supports now VT241 and epson-80 and may
   be reprogrammed for any other graphic device (Tek4014 etc).

